      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 20:49:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普瞄准漏洞 Temu，Shein 曾利用其对抗亚马逊</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/trump-tariffs-target-loophole-used-by-chinese-online-retailers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对中国、加拿大和墨西哥征收的新贸易税包括对国际电子商务的猛烈攻击，显然是计划取消长期以来对价值低于 800 美元的包裹的关税豁免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/trump-tariffs-target-loophole-used-by-chinese-online-retailers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 04:15:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通计划在关税担忧中交付价值 40 亿美元的美国黄金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/jpmorgan-plans-4-billion-gold-delivery-in-us-amid-tariff-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通公司将于 2 月份在纽约根据期货合约交付价值超过 40 亿美元的金条，而此时正值金价飙升和进口关税威胁引发全球范围内将黄金运往美国的浪潮。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/jpmorgan-plans-4-billion-gold-delivery-in-us-amid-tariff-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 18:12:26 GMT</pubDate>
